title: The service promises to inform and/or notify users regarding government inquiries that may involve users' personal data
quoteText:
We may share your information in response to a warrant, subpoena, or other court action, or if disclosure is necessary to protect our rights or the rights of the public at large.
We strive for transparency, and will notify you when possible
